Head On drops tonight at Midnight AEST. The inspiration for this song came during the darkest period for me last year, that very few know about. It’s mind blowing to me the things that happened in such a short time to get to this point. Moved across the world, found the right people, did the damn thing. I’m so proud of the fellas in @emotionpicture.au for being so ambitious with me. Thank you guys for everything we’ve accomplished so far. Sick one.

3. High school bedroom #2, Eugene, OR 
4. Portland, OR 
5. First apartment in Koreatown; LA, CA

7. Hollywood, Los Angeles
